OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHauliers and poultry       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers to get temporary   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fvisas                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Up to 10,500 lorry drivers and poultry 
OL,6, workers can receive temporary UK visas 
OL,7, as the government seeks to limit       
OL,8, disruption in the run-up to Christmas. 
OL,10,FThe government confirmed that 5,000    
OL,11,Ffuel tanker and food lorry drivers will
OL,12,Fbe eligible to work in the UK for three
OL,13,Fmonths, until Christmas Eve.           
OL,15,FThe scheme is also being extended to   
OL,16,F5,500 poultry workers.                 
OL,18,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said  
OL,19,Fit would "ensure preparations remain on
OL,20,Ftrack" for the festive season.         
